          "value": "קַבָּלַת שַׁבָּת\nKABBALAT SHABBAT - WELCOMING SHABBAT\nThis section, until Shalom Aleichem on page 142, does not offer alternative readings.\nPSALM 95:1-7",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
